ection, the teacher says goodbye using the phrase \'Hasta ___.\'','luego','[\"luego\", \"días\", \"noche\", \"mañana\"]',10,2,1,'2026-02-26 07:32:15.956563',18,NULL),(214,'translation','Як сказати \'Дякую за твою допомогу\' іспанською мовою?','Gracias por tu ayuda.','[\"Gracias por tu ayuda.\", \"Hasta luego, ha sido un placer.\", \"Nos vemos mañana.\", \"Buenos días, ¿cómo está usted?\"]',15,3,1,'2026-02-26 07:32:17.103602',18,NULL),(215,'ai_generated','Як ви попросите будь ласка людину, щоб вона передала вам сіль на іспанській мові?','¿Me pasas la sal, por favor?','[\"¿Me pasas la sal, por favor?\", \"¿Dónde está el baño?\", \"Hola, ¿qué tal?\", \"Disculpe, ¿sabe dónde está el baño?\"]',15,4,1,'2026-02-26 07:32:18.334988',18,NULL),(216,'multiple_choice','What is a key strategy to establish a strong connection during negotiations?','Using empathy and listening without interruptions.','[\"Using empathy and listening without interruptions.\", \"Presenting a highball offer at the start.\", \"Focusing solely on your own objectives.\", \"Avoiding any compromise.\"]',10,1,1,'2026-02-26 07:33:08.316196',6,NULL),(217,'fill_blank','To establish a strong connection during negotiations, it\'s crucial to actively ____________ without interruptions.','listen','[\"negotiate\", \"compromise\", \"listen\", \"assert\"]',10,2,1,'2026-02-26 07:33:09.381223',6,NULL),(218,'translation','Яка з наступних переговорних тактик має на меті досягнення взаємовигідного рішення для обох сторін?','Win-win','[\"Good cop, bad cop\", \"Win-win\", \"Highball/Lowball\", \"Hardball\"]',15,3,1,'2026-02-26 07:33:11.405389',6,NULL),(219,'ai_generated','Яка стратегія переговорів спрямована на досягнення взаємовигідного рішення для обох сторін?','Win-win','[\"Good cop, bad cop\", \"Win-win\", \"Highball/Lowball\", \"Playing hardball\"]',15,4,1,'2026-02-26 07:33:12.604867',6,NULL),(220,'multiple_choice','You need help with your bags at the airport. Which question should you ask?','\"Could you help me with my luggage?\"','[\"\\\"Where is the check-in counter for [airline]?\\\"\", \"\\\"Could you help me with my luggage?\\\"\", \"\\\"I think my flight is delayed.\\\"\", \"\\\"This layover is killing me!\\\"\"]',10,1,1,'2026-02-26 07:33:44.445936',10,NULL),(221,'fill_blank','Complete the sentence: The flight to London will depart from _____ 21.','gate',NULL,10,2,1,'2026-02-26 07:33:45.608578',10,NULL),(222,'translation','What should you be ready with while approaching the gate for your flight?','Boarding pass','[\"Passport\", \"Luggage tag\", \"Boarding pass\", \"Reservation number\"]',15,3,1,'2026-02-26 07:33:46.635849',10,NULL),(223,'ai_generated','Which document should you have ready when approaching the boarding area?','Boarding pass','[\"Boarding pass\", \"Luggage tag\", \"Check-in confirmation\", \"Passport\"]',15,4,1,'2026-02-26 07:33:47.689012',10,NULL),(224,'multiple_choice','Яке з наступних речень відображає ділову ситуацію з уроку?','Wir müssen unsere Strategie überdenken, um den Marktanteil zu erhöhen.','[\"Lass uns einen Slot für die Telko finden.\", \"Können Sie mir das Angebot bis zum Ende der Woche zusenden?\", \"Wir müssen unsere Strategie überdenken, um den Marktanteil zu erhöhen.\", \"Das Meeting wurde auf nächste Woche verschoben.\"]',10,1,1,'2026-02-26 07:34:29.585633',13,NULL),(225,'fill_blank','Як німецькою буде слово \'стратегія\' у контексті ділового спілкування?','Strategie','[\"Market\", \"Strategie\", \"Termin\", \"Angebot\"]',10,2,1,'2026-02-26 07:34:30.649783',13,NULL),(226,'translation','Виберіть правильний переклад виразу **\"Wir müssen unsere Strategie überdenken, um den Marktanteil zu erhöhen.\"**','We need to rethink our strategy to increase market share.','[\"We need to increase our sales volume.\", \"We need to find time for a telephone conference.\", \"We need to rethink our strategy to increase market share.\", \"We need to set a date for the meeting.\"]',15,3,1,'2026-02-26 07:34:32.506151',13,NULL),(227,'ai_generated','Виберіть правильне слово, щоб завершити речення: \'Unser Ziel ist es, die _____ zu steigern.\'','Verkaufszahlen','[\"Strategie\", \"Meeting\", \"Verkaufszahlen\", \"Marktanteil\"]',15,4,1,'2026-02-26 07:34:33.682569',13,NULL),(228,'multiple_choice','How do you call a task that is waiting to be started?','Backlog','[\"Backlog\", \"Sprint\", \"Fix\", \"Merge\"]',10,1,0,'2026-02-27 08:10:15.991210',33,NULL),(229,'translation','Translate: \"Я працюю над виправленням багу\"','I am working on fixing a bug',NULL,10,2,0,'2026-02-27 08:10:15.993664',33,NULL),(230,'translation','Як спитати \"Де я знайду молоко?\"','Wo finde ich Milch?',NULL,10,1,0,'2026-02-27 08:10:16.001837',34,NULL),(231,'multiple_choice','Що означає \"Kassenbon\"?','Чек','[\"Чек\", \"Пакет\", \"Гроші\", \"Знижка\"]',10,2,0,'2026-02-27 08:10:16.003942',34,NULL),(232,'multiple_choice','How do you ask for the bill?','La cuenta, por favor','[\"La cuenta, por favor\", \"Hola\", \"Gracias\", \"Perdón\"]',10,1,0,'2026-02-27 08:10:16.009959',35,NULL),(233,'translation','Translate: \"Стіл для двох\"','Una mesa para dos',NULL,10,2,0,'2026-02-27 08:10:16.012534',35,NULL),(234,'multiple_choice','Which word means \"a budget\"?','Un budget','[\"Un budget\", \"Une dépense\", \"Un profit\", \"Une perte\"]',10,1,0,'2026-02-27 08:10:16.018945',36,NULL),(235,'translation','Translate: \"Ми маємо обговорити дедлайни\"','Nous devons discuter des délais',NULL,10,2,0,'2026-02-27 08:10:16.020503',36,NULL),(236,'multiple_choice','What is a \'value proposition\'?','The unique value a product gives to customers','[\"The price of the product\", \"The unique value a product gives to customers\", \"The target market demographic\", \"A legal business contract\"]',10,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:37:56.288628',43,NULL),(237,'fill_blank','Our startup has gained significant _______ since launching last month.','traction',NULL,15,2,0,'2026-03-26 11:37:56.289629',43,NULL),(238,'multiple_choice','Which phrase is commonly used in Mexico to say \'What\'s up?\'','¿Qué onda?','[\"¿Qué tal?\", \"¿Qué onda?\", \"¿Qué pasa?\", \"¿Cómo andas?\"]',10,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:37:56.297464',44,NULL),(239,'translation','Translate to street Spanish (Spain): \'What\'s up?\'','¿Qué pasa?',NULL,20,2,0,'2026-03-26 11:37:56.300079',44,NULL),(240,'fill_blank','Je _________ un croissant, s\'il vous plaît.','voudrais',NULL,15,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:37:56.307405',45,NULL),(241,'multiple_choice','If your friend tells a crazy story and asks \'Do you think I\'m lying?\', how would you respond using internet slang?','No cap, I believe you.','[\"I am salty.\", \"No cap, I believe you.\", \"Spill the coffee.\", \"Where is your hat?\"]',15,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:40:47.604113',46,NULL),(242,'fill_blank','Stop hiding the details! Come on, spill the ________!','tea',NULL,10,2,0,'2026-03-26 11:40:47.606113',46,NULL),(243,'multiple_choice','Your friend is starting a very difficult exam. Which movie quote is perfect for wishing them luck?','May the Force be with you.','[\"I\'ll be back.\", \"May the Force be with you.\", \"We are not in Kansas.\", \"Here\'s looking at you, kid.\"]',20,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:40:47.612631',47,NULL),(244,'translation','Translate to German: \'A liter of beer, please!\'','Ein Maß Bier, bitte!',NULL,20,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:40:47.620008',48,NULL),(245,'multiple_choice','What is the most important rule when saying \'Prost!\' in Germany?','You must look the person in the eyes','[\"You must stand up\", \"You must look the person in the eyes\", \"You must clink glasses twice\", \"You must finish your drink\"]',15,2,0,'2026-03-26 11:40:47.621356',48,NULL),(246,'fill_blank','The Mona Lisa is a true ________ (masterpiece).','capolavoro',NULL,20,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:40:47.628302',49,NULL),(247,'multiple_choice','What does the technique \'sfumato\' refer to?','A soft painting technique without harsh outlines','[\"A type of canvas\", \"A soft painting technique without harsh outlines\", \"A method for mixing oil colors\", \"Painting rapidly before plaster dries\"]',15,2,0,'2026-03-26 11:40:47.630307',49,NULL),(248,'multiple_choice','If a song is extremely good, what is the best internet slang term to describe it?','It slaps','[\"It is salty\", \"It slaps\", \"It spills the tea\", \"It ghosts\"]',10,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:46:35.247305',50,NULL),(249,'multiple_choice','What does the acronym \'FOMO\' stand for?','Fear Of Missing Out','[\"For Our Main Objective\", \"Fear Of Missing Out\", \"Find Only My Opinions\", \"Face On My Own\"]',10,2,0,'2026-03-26 11:46:35.256771',50,NULL),(250,'multiple_choice','What is a \'Maß\' in the context of Oktoberfest?','A one-liter glass of beer','[\"A traditional German dance\", \"A one-liter glass of beer\", \"A roasted chicken\", \"A German folk song\"]',10,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:46:35.264932',51,NULL),(251,'multiple_choice','What is the strict rule when saying \'Prost!\' (Cheers) in Germany?','You must look the other person directly in the eyes','[\"You must stand on the table\", \"You must look the other person directly in the eyes\", \"You must drink the entire glass at once\", \"You must avoid eye contact\"]',10,2,0,'2026-03-26 11:46:35.265933',51,NULL),(252,'multiple_choice','In startup terminology, what does \'Traction\' refer to?','Measurable evidence of customer growth or revenue','[\"The design of your logo\", \"Measurable evidence of customer growth or revenue\", \"The initial problem you are trying to solve\", \"The amount of money you want to raise\"]',10,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:46:35.274573',52,NULL),(253,'multiple_choice','If you are traveling in Mexico, what is the most common slang word for \'dude\' or \'bro\'?','Güey','[\"Tío\", \"Che\", \"Güey\", \"Parce\"]',10,1,0,'2026-03-26 11:46:35.285435',53,NULL),(254,'multiple_choice','While studying English Through Pop Culture, you come across the term \'Easter egg\' frequently. What does it refer to in the context of pop culture?','A hidden message, inside joke, or secret feature in a movie, video game, or other form of media','[\"A type of chocolate treat enjoyed during Easter\", \"A popular dance move in music videos\", \"A character from a famous TV show\", \"A type of movie genre\"]',20,1,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:32.010725',NULL,10),(255,'multiple_choice','During a recent final exam, students were asked to analyze the lyrics of a popular song and identify which literary device was used in the chorus. What aspect of English Through Pop Culture does this question mainly focus on?','Analyzing pop song lyrics for literary devices','[\"Translating song lyrics\", \"Identifying musical instruments in a song\", \"Discussing the artist\'s biography\", \"Interpreting dance moves in a music video\"]',20,2,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:34.419938',NULL,10),(256,'fill_blank','While studying English Through Pop Culture, you came across the term \'Easter egg\' several times. What does \'Easter egg\' refer to in the context of pop culture?','A hidden message, image, or feature in a movie, video game, or software','[\"A traditional Easter gift\", \"A popular Easter dessert\", \"A hidden message, image, or feature in a movie, video game, or software\", \"A type of Easter decoration\"]',20,3,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:37.946082',NULL,10),(257,'multiple_choice','While studying English Through Pop Culture, you come across a term \'Binge-watching\'. What does it mean in the context of TV shows and series?','Watching multiple episodes of a show in one sitting','[\"Watching TV shows on a schedule\", \"Watching TV shows in random order\", \"Watching TV shows with subtitles\", \"Watching TV shows on different devices\"]',20,4,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:40.319269',NULL,10),(258,'multiple_choice','While studying English Through Pop Culture, you came across the term \'easter egg.\' What does this term refer to in pop culture?','Hidden message, reference, or inside joke placed in a movie, book, or video game for fans to find','[\"Traditional Easter celebration in pop culture\", \"Main character in a popular TV show\", \"A new type of candy popular in movies\", \"A type of music genre\"]',20,5,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:41.346931',NULL,10),(259,'fill_blank','Durante il Rinascimento, chi è stato uno dei più grandi artisti italiani che ha dipinto La Gioconda, un\'opera d\'arte famosissima in tutto il mondo?','Leonardo da Vinci','[\"Michelangelo\", \"Raffaello\", \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"Caravaggio\"]',20,1,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:43.568840',NULL,11),(260,'multiple_choice','Which Italian Renaissance artist is known for painting the ceiling of the Sistine Chapel in the Vatican?','Michelangelo','[\"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"Raphael\", \"Caravaggio\", \"Michelangelo\"]',20,2,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:45.859480',NULL,11),(261,'multiple_choice','Chi è considerato il padre della lingua italiana e autore della Divina Commedia?','Dante Alighieri','[\"Petrarca\", \"Boccaccio\", \"Dante Alighieri\", \"Leonardo da Vinci\"]',20,3,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:47.930117',NULL,11),(262,'fill_blank','Chi è l\'artista rinascimentale italiano conosciuto per i suoi affreschi nella Cappella Sistina a Roma?','Michelangelo','[\"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"Raffaello Sanzio\", \"Caravaggio\", \"Michelangelo\"]',20,4,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:49.049358',NULL,11),(263,'multiple_choice','Quale artista italiano è noto per il suo capolavoro \'La Gioconda\' esposto al Louvre di Parigi?','Leonardo da Vinci','[\"Michelangelo\", \"Raffaello\", \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"Caravaggio\"]',20,5,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:49.930998',NULL,11),(264,'multiple_choice','Du bist auf dem Oktoberfest und möchtest ein Bier bestellen. Welchen Satz verwendest du?','Ein Bier, bitte.','[\"Kann ich ein Bier haben?\", \"Ist das ein Bier?\", \"Bier ist lecker.\", \"Mein Bier ist kalt.\"]',20,1,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:52.211115',NULL,12),(265,'multiple_choice','You arrive at Oktoberfest and want to order a beer. Which phrase should you use to ask for \'one beer\' in German?','Ein Bier, bitte','[\"Ein Wasser, bitte\", \"Zwei Bier, bitte\", \"Danke schön\", \"Guten Tag\"]',20,2,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:53.276514',NULL,12),(266,'fill_blank','Während des Oktoberfestes in München trinken die Menschen traditionell viel ____________.','Bier','[\"Wein\", \"Wasser\", \"Kaffee\", \"Limonade\"]',20,3,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:54.173820',NULL,12),(267,'multiple_choice','You arrive at the Oktoberfest and want to order a beer. What phrase should you use to ask for one in German?','Ein Bier, bitte.','[\"Eine Cola, bitte.\", \"Ein Wasser, bitte.\", \"Ein Bier, bitte.\", \"Ein Kaffee, bitte.\"]',20,4,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:55.160350',NULL,12),(268,'fill_blank','Während des Oktoberfests in München trinken die Besucher typischerweise... (вираз, що означає \'drink\')','Bier','[\"Wasser\", \"Kaffee\", \"Tee\", \"Bier\"]',20,5,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:56.227662',NULL,12),(269,'multiple_choice','En Français pour les Gourmets, quel terme utilise-t-on pour décrire un plat préparé avec des ingrédients de la plus haute qualité et souvent préparé avec soin par un chef expérimenté?','Gastronomique','[\"Délicieux\", \"Bon marché\", \"Simple\", \"Épicé\"]',20,1,1,'2026-03-29 09:56:57.421487',NULL,13),(270,'fill_blank','Dans le cadre de l\'examen final couvrant tous les aspects de Français pour les Gourmets, comment peut-on décrire un plat en français pour exprimer qu\'il est très savoureux et délicieux?','Ce plat est un délice!','[\"Ce plat est très grand.\", \"Ce plat est très cher.\", \"Ce plat est très salé.\", \"Ce plat est un délice!\"]',20,2,1,'2026-03-29 09:57:00.918396',NULL,13),(271,'multiple_choice','Vous organisez un dîner français pour vos amis et vous voulez impressionner avec un plat traditionnel. Que préparez-vous si vous voulez servir un plat à base de viande hachée et d\'oignons caramélisés enveloppés dans de la pâte feuilletée ?','Bœuf en croûte','[\"Ratatouille\", \"Bœuf en croûte\", \"Coq au vin\", \"Escargots de Bourgogne\"]',20,3,1,'2026-03-29 09:57:02.382223',NULL,13),(272,'multiple_choice','Vous organisez un dîner français pour vos amis et vous souhaitez servir une soupe à l\'oignon. Comment dites-vous \'soupe à l\'oignon\' en français?','Soupe à l\'oignon','[\"Soupe aux champignons\", \"Soupe à la tomate\", \"Soupe au potiron\", \"Soupe à l\'oignon\"]',20,4,1,'2026-03-29 09:57:03.562463',NULL,13),(273,'multiple_choice','Which of the following is the most appropriate formal closing for a business email when you don\'t know the recipient\'s name?','Yours faithfully','[\"Cheers\", \"Best regards\", \"Yours faithfully\", \"Talk soon\"]',10,1,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.264425',NULL,23),(274,'fill_blank','I am looking forward ___ (to) meeting you next week. Fill in the missing preposition.','to',NULL,10,2,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.266545',NULL,23),(275,'multiple_choice','In a professional context, what does the acronym \'BCC\' stand for in an email header?','Blind Carbon Copy','[\"Business Carbon Copy\", \"Blind Carbon Copy\", \"Basic Communication Code\", \"Brief Corporate Chat\"]',10,3,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.270653',NULL,23),(276,'fill_blank','Could you please ___ (send) me the latest sales report by the end of the day? Fill in the missing verb.','send',NULL,10,4,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.273721',NULL,23),(277,'multiple_choice','When scheduling a meeting or an event, what does \'TBA\' usually mean?','To Be Announced','[\"To Be Announced\", \"Totally Basic Agreement\", \"Time Between Acts\", \"Technical Board Assessment\"]',10,5,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.276853',NULL,23),(278,'multiple_choice','Which of these words is a synonym for \'postpone\' in a business setting?','Defer','[\"Advance\", \"Defer\", \"Hasten\", \"Implement\"]',10,6,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.278363',NULL,23),(279,'fill_blank','We need to hammer ___ (out) the final details of the contract before signing. Fill in the missing particle.','out',NULL,10,7,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.280363',NULL,23),(280,'multiple_choice','Which phrase is commonly used to start a formal business meeting?','Let\'s get down to business.','[\"What\'s up guys?\", \"Let\'s get down to business.\", \"Why are we here?\", \"Tell me a joke.\"]',10,8,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.283875',NULL,23),(281,'fill_blank','I\'m sorry, I didn\'t quite catch that. Could you please ___ (repeat) what you just said? Fill in the missing verb.','repeat',NULL,10,9,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.287413',NULL,23),(282,'multiple_choice','What does the abbreviation \'EOD\' stand for in business communication?','End Of Day','[\"End Of Day\", \"Each Other\'s Data\", \"Early Out Draft\", \"Electronic Office Document\"]',10,10,0,'2026-03-29 10:01:37.290414',NULL,23);
